# Project Stack

## Client-side libraries (mandatory)

| Concern | Library | Do not use |
|---------|---------|------------|
| Data fetching | TanStack Query (`@tanstack/react-query`) | `useEffect` + `fetch`, SWR, raw `fetch` in components |
| Global client state | Zustand | Redux, Context for app-wide state, Jotai |
| Tables | TanStack Table (`@tanstack/react-table`) | Hand-rolled `<table>` with sort/pagination logic |
| Forms | TanStack Form (`@tanstack/react-form`) | `react-hook-form`, native uncontrolled forms |
| UI / design | shadcn/ui (`components/ui/`) | Custom buttons/inputs, hardcoded colors, overriding shadcn spacing |

## Server vs client boundary

- **Server Components** (default): auth, DB access (Prisma), initial page data, Server Actions.
- **Client Components** (`"use client"`): TanStack Query hooks, Zustand, TanStack Table/Form, interactive UI.
- Fetch on the client only through TanStack Query. Prefetch in Server Components when SSR/hydration is needed.

## File locations

- `lib/query/` — query client, query keys, shared query/mutation options
- `hooks/` — custom hooks wrapping `useQuery` / `useMutation`
- `lib/stores/` — Zustand stores
- `components/data-table/` — shared table primitives
- `lib/schemas/` — Zod schemas (shared by forms and server validation)
